						<div class="postbody">With MMC5, you could use 16x16 tiles freely, since you can pick from a much larger group of tiles with that mapper.<br />Or you could make up a new MMC5 variant where you make the most significant bit of CHR bankswitching pick a RAM chip instead (like TQROM for MMC3).<br />But the emulators won't know about that until it's programmed into them.<br /><br />Your image isn't loading, so attach it here.  Edit: now it is loading...</div>

					
